    <h3>{l s='How to receive copy of emails ?' mod='everpsmailcopy'}</h3>
    <p>{l s='First, an employee account is required on the store. Do not hesitate to create one with the desired profile in order to receive copies of emails.' mod='everpsmailcopy'}</p>
    <p>{l s='Once the account is created, simply add it in the module configuration by selecting it in the dedicated field' mod='everpsmailcopy'}</p>
    <p>{l s='You can choose to receive all emails sent (apart from those sent to employees) or only emails sent to customers registered on your store.' mod='everpsmailcopy'}</p>
    <p>{l s='To do this, check or uncheck the Yes / No box present in the module configuration' mod='everpsmailcopy'}</p>
    <p>{l s='You can fill in several employee accounts, the emails will be sent in BCC hidden copy to each of the accounts saved in this module' mod='everpsmailcopy'}</p>
